Usage: deletePinGroup [-help] [-cell <string>] -pinGroup <string>

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>         # Specifies the name of the module.The module name is
                       # not required if the command is run on a top-level
                       # module. (string, optional)
-pinGroup <string>     # Specifies the name of the pin group that was created.
                       # (string, required)